674
00:44:34,683 --> 00:44:36,268
<b>That's just me.</b>

675
00:44:37,102 --> 00:44:38,520
<b>My nerves.</b>

676
00:44:39,146 --> 00:44:41,523
<b>- Where do you usually live?
- On the Left Bank.</b>

677
00:44:41,774 --> 00:44:44,360
<b>- Better than here, I bet.
