777
00:50:27,637 --> 00:50:29,598
<b>Even though they slept together.</b>

778
00:50:30,098 --> 00:50:31,141
<b>You have proof?</b>

779
00:50:31,558 --> 00:50:34,436
<b>- Your husband has them watched.
