788
00:50:56,417 --> 00:50:59,546
<b>When you can't see,
your imagination runs wild.</b>

789
00:51:01,005 --> 00:51:05,594
<b>How sad, this poor guy
who can't afford curtains!</b>

790
00:51:09,889 --> 00:51:11,766
<b>- How is he?
