794
00:51:19,651 --> 00:51:22,028
<b>I saw the grocer's wife
for her phlebitis.</b>

795
00:51:22,279 --> 00:51:25,239
<b>The shot she gave me was a joy!</b>

796
00:51:25,864 --> 00:51:28,618
<b>- Do you have bronchitis?
