00:51:34,040 --> 00:51:35,292
<b>So keep it up.</b>

800
00:51:37,085 --> 00:51:39,254
<b>Coming to Andre's birthday?</b>

801
00:51:39,504 --> 00:51:40,839
<b>I have a ton of work.</b>

802
00:51:41,089 --> 00:51:42,716
<b>Stop by to please Francois.</b>

803
00:51:42,966 --> 00:51:46,136
