805
00:51:59,901 --> 00:52:00,943
<b>Because she won't.</b>

806
00:52:01,319 --> 00:52:03,946
<b>I hope you're wrong:
He must be so unhappy.</b>

807
00:52:04,196 --> 00:52:07,074
<b>Holed up in his place
with his heartache.</b>

808
00:53:29,412 --> 00:53:30,162
<b>Bravo!</b>

809
00:54:26,513 --> 00:54:28,973
<b>Karl, bravo.</b>

810
00:54:29,224 --> 00:54:30,266
<b>Thank you for coming.</b>

811
00:54:30,516 --> 00:54:32,394
<b>One of your finest collections!</b>

812
00:54:32,644 --> 00:54:35,439
<b>On to the next! I'm never satisfied.</b>

813
00:54:56,086 --> 00:54:57,379
<b>Not too bored?</b>

814
00:54:57,629 --> 00:54:59,464
<b>Why do you all walk like horses?</b>

815
00:55:07,806 --> 00:55:09,558
<b>We did our job, let's go.</b>

816
00:55:12,018 --> 00:55:15,064
