<b>A what?</b>

885
00:58:33,522 --> 00:58:35,900
<b>An act, a game,
you're just a stand-in.</b>

886
00:58:36,150 --> 00:58:39,696
<b>We paid you to pretend
you were a couple, not to be one.</b>

887
00:58:40,446 --> 00:58:41,948
<b>People were watching us.</b>

888
00:58:42,198 --> 00:58:44,159
<b>She was sick of it,
hence the curtains.</b>

889
00:58:44,409 --> 00:58:46,911
<b>We have peace,
they can think what they want.</b>

890
00:58:47,287 --> 00:58:50,873
<b>You're exploiting us, scumbag!
You'll regret it!</b>

891
00:58:51,123 --> 00:58:51,583
<b>Who is this?</b>

892
00:58:51,833 --> 00:58:54,670
<b>I paid you! You thief, you thug!</b>

893
00:58:56,004 --> 00:58:56,922
<b>Hello?</b>

894
00:58:57,965 --> 00:58:59,424
<b>I hung up, sir.</b>

895
00:59:00,592 --> 00:59:01,718
<b>I did it.</b>

896
00:59:05,515 --> 00:59:07,724
<b>Don't lose your temper like that.</b>

897
00:59:08,476 --> 00:59:10,603
<b>Calm down,</b>

898
00:59:10,936 --> 00:59:13,398
<b>analyze the situation coolly.</b>

899
00:59:15,608 --> 00:59:16,693
<b>That guy's sick!</b>

900
00:59:22,782 --> 00:59:25,077
<b>It's 8PM, we're dining
at the Lambert's.</b>

901
00:59:25,327 --> 00:59:27,912
<b>I'll let you go alone,
I don't feel well.</b>

902
00:59:28,162 --> 00:59:28,831
<b>Are you sick?</b>

903
00:59:29,414 --> 00:59:31,667
<b>Tired. I've had some rough days.</b>

904
00:59:31,917 --> 00:59:34,128
<b>Sorry, but I don't feel up to it.</b>

905
00:59:34,419 --> 00:59:35,879
<b>True, you do seem tired.</b>

906
00:59:36,130 --> 00:59:38,465
<b>It takes real stress
to look that way.</b>

907
00:59:39,091 --> 00:59:40,926
<b>Apologize to the Lamberts for me.</b>

908
00:59:41,427 --> 00:59:42,928
<b>Should I cancel?</b>

909
00:59:43,178 --> 00:59:45,432
<b>I can stay
and hear of your troubles.</b>

910
00:59:45,974 --> 00:59:48,767
<b>Forget my troubles,
I'm tired, that's all.</b>

911
00:59:49,018 --> 00:59:51,313
<b>Don't lie,
I know what's upsetting you.</b>

912
00:59:54,316 --> 00:59:55,817
<b>That strike in the factory.</b>

913
00:59:57,527 --> 00:59:59,195
<b>It hasn't made life easier.</b>

914
01:00:00,530 --> 01:00:01,740
<b>I'm so sorry, poor dear.</b>

915
01:00:02,909 --> 01:00:03,993
<b>You'll be late.</b>

916
01:00:04,535 --> 01:00:05,869
<b>Get some rest!</b>

917
01:00:06,786 --> 01:00:08,205
<b>See you later.</b>

918
01:00:16,422 --> 01:00:18,674
<b>A guy insulted me
over your curtains.</b>

919
01:00:18,925 --> 01:00:20,885
<b>Called me a scumbag and a thug.</b>

920
01:00:23,555 --> 01:00:26,433
<b>- If you wanted curtains...
- But I didn't!</b>

921
01:00:26,683 --> 01:00:28,392
<b>- You didn't?
- No!</b>

922
01:00:28,601 --> 01:00:30,062
<b>Then, who?</b>

923
01:00:30,896 --> 01:00:33,315
<b>His wife. Only she would do it.</b>

924
01:00:33,565 --> 01:00:34,858
<b>His wife?</b>

925
01:00:35,275 --> 01:00:36,777
<b>Why'd she fix up my place?</b>

926
01:00:37,069 --> 01:00:38,987
<b>It's their problem. Not yours.</b>

927
01:00:39,237 --> 01:00:42,033
<b>It's my home,
I could file a complaint!</b>

928
01:00:42,825 --> 01:00:43,575
<b>No.</b>

929
01:00:44,284 --> 01:00:47,704
<b>Cops'll say: "What was stolen?"
"No, they hung curtains."</b>

930
01:00:47,955 --> 01:00:48,873
<b>Might turn ugly.</b>

931
01:00:49,415 --> 01:00:50,250
<b>And he called you?</b>

932
01:00:50,500 --> 01:00:54,045
<b>His lawyer did. Then that maniac
insulted me and hung up.</b>

933
01:00:57,131 --> 01:00:58,883
<b>She pulled it off.</b>

934
01:01:00,302 --> 01:01:01,761
<b>I'll be right back.</b>

935
01:01:09,228 --> 01:01:11,688
<b>Give it back.
Emilie won't take it, nor will I.</b>

936
01:01:12,480 --> 01:01:14,900
<b>Why? No one's asking
for the money back.</b>

937
01:01:15,150 --> 01:01:16,693
<b>He called me a thief, I'm not.</b>

938
01:01:16,944 --> 01:01:19,071
<b>32,450 Euros is a lot.
He'll want it.</b>

939
01:01:19,780 --> 01:01:22,993
<b>He's a billionaire,
that's a tip for him.</b>

940
01:01:23,325 --> 01:01:25,370
<b>No, he called me a thief!</b>

941
01:01:26,245 --> 01:01:28,163
<b>Give it to Emilie, she'll take it.</b>

942
01:01:28,456 --> 01:01:32,210
<b>It's over with Emilie.
Now she's with Mr Cell Phone.</b>

943
01:01:32,460 --> 01:01:33,545
<b>Francois...</b>

944
01:01:33,795 --> 01:01:35,505
<b>I'm sure she realizes</b>

945
01:01:35,755 --> 01:01:38,174
<b>she's losing a really great guy.</b>

946
01:01:49,227 --> 01:01:50,479
<b>I'm cold.</b>

947
01:01:54,567 --> 01:01:57,612
<b>Take my blanket, I'm not cold at all.</b>

948
01:01:58,571 --> 01:02:01,282
<b>No, I don't need it. Thanks, keep it.</b>

949
01:02:10,416 --> 01:02:11,835
<b>It's because of him?</b>

950
01:02:12,419 --> 01:02:15,172
<b>He's a bastard.
It's wrong to cheat on your wife.</b>

951
01:02:15,422 --> 01:02:18,007
<b>Wait till you're married to say that.</b>

952
01:02:19,426 --> 01:02:21,429
<b>Why am I so cold?</b>

953
01:02:28,435 --> 01:02:32,482
<b>All the men I meet are creeps
with a one-track mind.</b>

954
01:02:41,950 --> 01:02:45,536
<b>If we stay any longer like this,
I'll turn into one, too.</b>

955
01:02:51,376 --> 01:02:54,088
<b>Go back to bed, I feel better.</b>

956
01:03:03,932 --> 01:03:04,890
<b>Thanks.</b>

957
01:03:12,274 --> 01:03:13,650
<b>- What's that?
- Nothing.</b>

958
01:03:14,776 --> 01:03:17,112
<b>You said not to talk about it,
so I won't.</b>

959
01:03:17,779 --> 01:03:19,447
<b>They're getting married.</b>

960
01:03:20,448 --> 01:03:21,324
<b>What?</b>

961
01:03:21,741 --> 01:03:24,703
<b>Their picture's in here,
she's in a wedding dress.</b>

962
01:03:24,953 --> 01:03:27,415
<b>But you're right,
it's their business.</b>

963
01:03:27,665 --> 01:03:30,959
<b>Do the new pens go in the rack
or at the register?</b>

964
01:03:31,210 --> 01:03:34,463
<b>He won't marry her.
I'm the one he loves, he said so.</b>

965
01:03:34,714 --> 01:03:36,882
<b>- Don't bring that up again.
- I didn't.</b>

966
01:03:37,508 --> 01:03:39,719
<b>Never again! Is that clear?</b>

967
01:03:40,636 --> 01:03:43,599
<b>It's for you.
Can we talk? Got a minute?</b>

968
01:03:44,141 --> 01:03:45,600
<b>Go get a coffee.</b>

969
01:03:46,058 --> 01:03:48,936
<b>- Did you hear? Get a coffee!
- OK.</b>

970
01:03:56,861 --> 01:03:57,946
<b>Thanks.</b>

971
01:04:01,199 --> 01:04:01,700
<b>Well?</b>

972
01:04:02,118 --> 01:04:03,118
<b>She's still there.</b>

973
01:04:03,368 --> 01:04:05,747
<b>If she'd pose
for a picture for my window.</b>

974
01:04:06,331 --> 01:04:08,458
<b>Bad timing.
Whatever they're saying,</b>

975
01:04:08,708 --> 01:04:10,167
<b>it's heavy.</b>

976
01:04:10,585 --> 01:04:11,919
<b>Means another lunch alone.</b>

977
01:04:13,379 --> 01:04:14,672
<b>You had a date with her?</b>

978
01:04:14,923 --> 01:04:17,425
<b>She cancels all the time.
She can't like me.</b>

979
01:04:17,675 --> 01:04:18,468
<b>Weird, huh?</b>

980
01:04:18,718 --> 01:04:22,805
<b>Yeah. A handsome guy like you
shouldn't lunch alone.</b>

981
01:04:26,225 --> 01:04:28,394
<b>- What sign is she?
- Who?</b>

982
01:04:28,812 --> 01:04:29,855
<b>You!</b>

983
01:04:30,564 --> 01:04:32,273
<b>Aries, Gemini rising.</b>

984
01:04:32,524 --> 01:04:34,985
<b>That's very good.
Let's see your hand.</b>

985
01:04:39,031 --> 01:04:41,659
<b>- You're very sensual...
- Really?</b>

986
01:04:41,909 --> 01:04:44,412
<b>Being fleshy there means you're hot.</b>

987
01:04:44,913 --> 01:04:46,163
<b>Let's see yours.</b>

988
01:04:50,501 --> 01:04:51,920
<b>I never saw that before.</b>

989
01:04:52,169 --> 01:04:53,505
<b>Me neither.</b>

990
01:04:56,633 --> 01:04:58,134
<b>Wanna have lunch?</b>

991
01:05:03,432 --> 01:05:04,808
<b>There you're lovely...</b>

992
01:05:05,058 --> 01:05:06,310
<b>Great.</b>

993
01:05:07,185 --> 01:05:08,396
<b>Perfect.</b>

994
01:05:08,646 --> 01:05:10,647
<b>Let's do a few more.</b>

995
01:05:12,232 --> 01:05:13,317
<b>Like that.</b>

996
01:05:14,151 --> 01:05:16,237
<b>Let's take a break!</b>

997
01:05:22,034 --> 01:05:23,787
<b>I'm not wild
about the collections this year.</b>

998
01:05:24,037 --> 01:05:27,290
<b>Only the big names
held their own...</b>

999
01:05:27,540 --> 01:05:31,086
<b>The young ones were all
rags and tatters. Diddly poo!</b>

1000
01:05:31,544 --> 01:05:33,422
<b>As for Elena! Seen her guy?</b>

1001
01:05:34,922 --> 01:05:36,049
<b>Look!</b>

1002
01:05:37,467 --> 01:05:40,387
<b>He's a parking valet! Elena, with him?</b>

1003
01:05:40,637 --> 01:05:42,055
<b>He has no money, no looks!</b>

1004
01:05:42,514 --> 01:05:44,100
<b>What does she see in him?</b>

1005
01:05:44,850 --> 01:05:48,563
<b>He must have hidden talents.
That's gotta be it.</b>

1006
01:05:49,438 --> 01:05:50,898
<b>Something huge!</b>

1007
01:05:54,192 --> 01:05:55,819
<b>Things OK, Richard?</b>

1008
01:05:58,489 --> 01:06:00,533
<b>- You OK?
- Sure. When's the wedding?</b>

1009
01:06:00,784 --> 01:06:02,827
<b>That's just fan-mag bullshit.</b>

1010
01:06:03,077 --> 01:06:04,579
<b>- Can I ask you a favor?
- Sure.</b>

1011
01:06:04,787 --> 01:06:06,790
<b>When you're married, don't eat here.</b>

1012
01:06:07,040 --> 01:06:08,626
<b>I'd hate parking your car.</b>

1013
01:06:08,917 --> 01:06:09,792
<b>- Richard...
- What?</b>

1014
01:06:10,044 --> 01:06:12,211
<b>There's nothing between Elena and me.</b>

1015
01:06:12,546 --> 01:06:13,254
<b>Sure.</b>

1016
01:06:13,504 --> 01:06:15,841
<b>I can't explain now, but soon I will.</b>

1017
01:06:16,091 --> 01:06:17,717
<b>You'll see, it was no big deal.</b>

1018
01:06:18,052 --> 01:06:19,970
<b>- You're just ashamed.
- Of what?</b>

1019
01:06:20,220 --> 01:06:22,431
<b>Kicking me out
to ball a supermodel.</b>

1020
01:06:22,681 --> 01:06:25,935
<b>Now you're marrying her,
and I'm stuck at my drunken mom's.</b>

1021
01:06:26,226 --> 01:06:28,020
<b>I'm not ashamed or marrying anyone.</b>

1022
01:06:28,229 --> 01:06:29,939
<b>I bet you gave her Emilie's ring.</b>

1023
01:06:30,189 --> 01:06:32,150
<b>You're a dog,
that's why you get laid.</b>

1024
01:06:32,442 --> 01:06:34,027
<b>But you're not happy.</b>

1025
01:06:34,277 --> 01:06:35,487
<b>I'm not getting laid!</b>

1026
01:06:37,781 --> 01:06:39,616
<b>This thing with Elena's a fraud.</b>

1027
01:06:39,866 --> 01:06:41,701
<b>I'm telling you, you're my buddy.</b>

1028
01:06:41,910 --> 01:06:43,536
<b>Soon we'll be living together again.</b>

1029
01:06:45,622 --> 01:06:46,539
<b>You shitting me?</b>

1030
01:06:47,165 --> 01:06:48,793
<b>You have my word.</b>

1031
01:06:51,127 --> 01:06:52,838
<b>You're an ass-face, but I like you.</b>

1032
01:06:55,216 --> 01:06:56,299
<b>Thanks, Francois.</b>

1033
01:07:04,016 --> 01:07:06,227
<b>Don't park it, I'll only be a minute.</b>

1034
01:07:06,435 --> 01:07:07,728
<b>Is Mr. Pignon around?</b>

1035
01:07:08,188 --> 01:07:09,063
<b>Yes, he's here.</b>

1036
01:07:13,234 --> 01:07:14,068
<b>It's for you!</b>

1037
01:07:36,593 --> 01:07:37,135
<b>Bastard!</b>

1038
01:07:37,385 --> 01:07:41,014
<b>She gives me her number,
and I didn't ask for it.</b>

1039
01:07:46,770 --> 01:07:48,522
<b>Casanova, you about through?</b>

1040
01:07:48,771 --> 01:07:49,731
<b>Francois...</b>

1041
01:07:52,443 --> 01:07:53,443
<b>Francois.</b>

1042
01:08:11,004 --> 01:08:12,589
<b>Mrs Levasseur, sir.</b>

1043
01:08:13,840 --> 01:08:15,300
<b>Show her in.</b>

1044
01:08:19,220 --> 01:08:20,263
<b>You wanted to see me?</b>

1045
01:08:20,513 --> 01:08:23,141
<b>I haven't been here in ages.</b>

1046
01:08:23,391 --> 01:08:24,976
<b>I walked through the place.</b>

1047
01:08:25,226 --> 01:08:26,978
<b>A landlord's visit!</b>

1048
01:08:27,730 --> 01:08:28,855
<b>That's fine...</b>

1049
01:08:29,189 --> 01:08:31,067
<b>- Know what the gossip is?
- No.</b>

1050
01:08:31,317 --> 01:08:32,944
<b>Your mind's not on the job.</b>

1051
01:08:33,194 --> 01:08:34,402
<b>Screw the gossip.</b>

1052
01:08:35,321 --> 01:08:39,325
<b>And that if you keep it up,
you won't be CEO for long.</b>

1053
01:08:40,076 --> 01:08:41,619
<b>Got nothing funnier?</b>

1054
01:08:43,038 --> 01:08:46,166
<b>I had the curtains
put up at Pignon's.</b>

1055
01:08:50,462 --> 01:08:53,215
<b>Your lies about that photo
are such fun.</b>

1056
01:08:53,464 --> 01:08:55,175
<b>Your bumbling's hilarious.</b>

1057
01:08:55,467 --> 01:08:57,427
<b>I don't follow you.</b>

1058
01:08:57,678 --> 01:08:58,637
<b>Then I'll spell it out.</b>

1059
01:08:59,096 --> 01:09:00,681
<b>If you love that girl, leave me,</b>

1060
01:09:00,931 --> 01:09:03,016
<b>go off with her to Venice,</b>

1061
01:09:03,267 --> 01:09:04,810
<b>I'll file for a divorce.</b>

1062
01:09:05,185 --> 01:09:06,436
<b>What are you talking about?</b>

1063
01:09:06,687 --> 01:09:09,606
<b>A poor sap who wants
both a wife and a mistress.</b>

1064
01:09:09,856 --> 01:09:10,941
<b>It's time to choose.</b>

1065
01:09:11,191 --> 01:09:14,319
<b>Darling, I never planned
to divorce you.</b>

1066
01:09:15,488 --> 01:09:18,741
<b>You've been glum
since she lives with that guy.</b>

1067
01:09:19,032 --> 01:09:22,036
<b>She means nothing to me, it's over.</b>

1068
01:09:22,287 --> 01:09:23,955
<b>I'll go to Venice, but with you!</b>

1069
01:09:24,163 --> 01:09:25,915
<b>Once the Board meeting's over,</b>

1070
01:09:26,165 --> 01:09:29,003
<b>we'll leave on a second honeymoon.</b>

1071
01:09:29,253 --> 01:09:31,880
<b>We had a lovely suite
for our first one.</b>

1072
01:09:32,131 --> 01:09:33,339
<b>Try to book it again.</b>

1073
01:09:33,799 --> 01:09:34,842
<b>I'll get right on it.</b>

1074
01:10:06,792 --> 01:10:08,961
<b><i>I haven't been here in ages.</b></i>

1075
01:10:09,336 --> 01:10:11,255
<b><i>I walked through the place.</b></i>

1076
01:10:11,505 --> 01:10:12,964
<b><i>A landlord's visit!</b></i>

1077
01:10:23,893 --> 01:10:25,269
<b>Francois is marrying a model!</b>

1078
01:10:26,145 --> 01:10:26,812
<b>What?</b>

1079
01:10:27,063 --> 01:10:29,941
<b>I heard it at the beauty parlor.
They saw it in a paper.</b>

1080
01:10:30,191 --> 01:10:32,194
<b>He's marrying a very famous model.</b>

1081
01:10:32,444 --> 01:10:34,696
<b>- What's this?
- They forgot which paper,</b>

1082
01:10:35,154 --> 01:10:39,201
<b>but swore Francois
is marrying Naomi Campbell.</b>

1083
01:10:39,451 --> 01:10:40,452
<b>A name like that...</b>

1084
01:10:40,744 --> 01:10:42,120
<b>He'd have told you...</b>

1085
01:10:42,371 --> 01:10:44,289
<b>Why would Naomi Campbell
marry our kid?</b>

1086
01:10:44,539 --> 01:10:46,833
<b>It's not her, but someone famous...</b>

1087
01:10:47,042 --> 01:10:48,752
<b>I couldn't reach Francois at home.</b>

1088
01:10:49,002 --> 01:10:50,754
<b>But he was heartbroken over Emilie.</b>

1089
01:10:50,964 --> 01:10:52,923
<b>- I don't get it.
- Me, neither.</b>

1090
01:10:53,883 --> 01:10:54,926
<b>It's me!</b>

1091
01:10:57,053 --> 01:10:58,721
<b>Happy birthday, Dad!</b>

1092
01:11:00,473 --> 01:11:02,141
<b>Your hair looks great, Mom.</b>

1093
01:11:03,476 --> 01:11:05,186
<b>Why are you staring at me?</b>

1094
01:11:05,479 --> 01:11:07,356
<b>Are you marrying a model?</b>

1095
01:11:07,564 --> 01:11:09,315
<b>- No way!
- My hairdresser read it.</b>

1096
01:11:09,524 --> 01:11:11,150
<b>It's just fan-mag gossip.</b>

1097
01:11:11,401 --> 01:11:13,194
<b>Open your gift, Dad!</b>

1098
01:11:19,034 --> 01:11:20,160
<b>It's magnificent!</b>

1099
01:11:20,452 --> 01:11:22,037
<b>- You don't have that one?
- No.</b>

1100
01:11:22,288 --> 01:11:23,706
<b>Thanks, Francois.</b>

1101
01:11:23,956 --> 01:11:26,417
<b>My collection's becoming famous.</b>

1102
01:11:26,667 --> 01:11:29,920
<b>I'm invited to a dinner
to talk about my corkscrews!</b>

1103
01:11:30,170 --> 01:11:31,631
<b>That's great, Dad.</b>

1104
01:11:31,964 --> 01:11:33,758
<b>I brought a friend. That OK?</b>

1105
01:11:33,967 --> 01:11:34,925
<b>A friend?</b>

1106
01:11:41,850 --> 01:11:42,600
<b>Hello.</b>

1107
01:11:42,809 --> 01:11:43,311
<b>Elena.</b>

1108
01:11:43,561 --> 01:11:45,146
<b>Happy birthday, sir.</b>

1109
01:11:45,396 --> 01:11:46,271
<b>Can I help?</b>

1110
01:11:46,521 --> 01:11:49,066
<b>No, sit in the other room,
I'll handle it all.</b>

1111
01:11:52,486 --> 01:11:54,237
<b>Our sonny has a secret life.</b>

1112
01:11:54,446 --> 01:11:57,199
<b>Incredible.
Where'd he ever find that?</b>

1113
01:11:58,326 --> 01:12:01,078
<b>- My God, maybe it's Emilie.
- You said she wasn't coming.</b>

1114
01:12:01,287 --> 01:12:03,289
<b>- Hello.
- Hi, sweetheart.</b>

1115
01:12:03,915 --> 01:12:05,416
<b>He calls her "sweetheart"!</b>

1116
01:12:17,054 --> 01:12:19,181
<b>- Happy birthday!
- Thanks Emilie, dear.</b>

1117
01:12:19,473 --> 01:12:20,848
<b>Where's the oldie?</b>

1118
01:12:22,351 --> 01:12:23,852
<b>- Happy birthday.
- Thanks.</b>

1119
01:12:24,102 --> 01:12:27,148
<b>How old are you, around 75?</b>

1120
01:12:32,904 --> 01:12:36,157
<b>I'm 58. That guy's an idiot!</b>

1121
01:12:36,407 --> 01:12:38,076
<b>I'll change doctors.</b>

1122
01:12:38,743 --> 01:12:42,622
<b>What did I say?
He can get all the girls he wants!</b>

1123
01:12:43,040 --> 01:12:46,125
<b>About the 20 million,
I'm canceling the transfer.</b>

1124
01:12:52,800 --> 01:12:54,843
<b>I'll never see her again.</b>

1125
01:12:55,094 --> 01:12:57,137
<b>But to hold her one last time...</b>

1126
01:12:57,763 --> 01:13:00,474
<b>I went through that once.</b>

1127
01:13:00,808 --> 01:13:02,476
<b>I got my last time.</b>

1128
01:13:02,685 --> 01:13:05,688
<b>I lied to the girl,
told her what she wanted to hear.</b>

1129
01:13:05,938 --> 01:13:07,648
<b>She came to our date, elated.</b>

1130
01:13:07,898 --> 01:13:10,150
<b>I got a glorious last night with her.</b>

1131
01:13:10,818 --> 01:13:12,070
<b>That's odious.</b>

1132
01:13:12,653 --> 01:13:13,822
<b>I know.</b>

1133
01:13:14,280 --> 01:13:17,867
<b>"Happy birthday to you..."</b>

1134
01:13:40,182 --> 01:13:43,020
<b>- Doctor, may I ask you for something.
- What?</b>

1135
01:13:43,644 --> 01:13:44,562
<b>Your daughter's hand.</b>

1136
01:13:44,937 --> 01:13:46,690
<b>You should ask her.</b>

1137
01:13:47,148 --> 01:13:48,149
<b>I did.</b>

1138
01:13:48,399 --> 01:13:49,442
<b>Did she accept?</b>

1139
01:13:49,775 --> 01:13:50,318
<b>Yes.</b>

1140
01:13:51,068 --> 01:13:52,988
<b>Then why are you pestering me?</b>

1141
01:13:59,911 --> 01:14:00,912
<b>Thanks, Doctor.</b>

1142
01:14:11,507 --> 01:14:14,093
<b>Why's that doctor always angry?</b>

1143
01:14:14,301 --> 01:14:16,471
<b>He's allergic to patients.</b>

1144
01:14:18,014 --> 01:14:18,598
<b>Hello?</b>

1145
01:14:18,890 --> 01:14:21,099
<b>It's me, I have good news for you,</b>

1146
01:14:21,351 --> 01:14:23,019
<b>or rather, good news for us.</b>

1147
01:14:23,269 --> 01:14:23,770
<b>I'm listening.</b>

1148
01:14:23,979 --> 01:14:26,481
<b>No, I want to surprise you.</b>

1149
01:14:26,689 --> 01:14:28,316
<b>Can we meet tomorrow?</b>

1150
01:14:28,566 --> 01:14:30,485
<b>I've got a show,
but I'm free at 5PM.</b>

1151
01:14:30,693 --> 01:14:33,447
<b><i>- Where?
- At the Pavilion, in the Park.</b></i>

1152
01:14:33,780 --> 01:14:35,240
<b>I'll pick you up at five.</b>

1153
01:14:35,491 --> 01:14:38,869
<b>No, let's avoid the press,
meet me in the usual place.</b>

1154
01:14:39,119 --> 01:14:41,455
<b>Do I spend tonight
at his place or mine?</b>

1155
01:14:41,704 --> 01:14:44,166
<b><i>Go home, you're through
with that bum.</b></i>

1156
01:14:44,458 --> 01:14:45,751
<b>See you tomorrow, love.</b>

1157
01:14:47,795 --> 01:14:49,755
<b>Why does he keep insulting me?</b>

1158
01:14:50,005 --> 01:14:51,548
<b>Doesn't matter now.</b>

1159
01:14:52,175 --> 01:14:54,052
<b>I'm happy, Francois.</b>

1160
01:14:54,761 --> 01:14:57,555
<b>Then he can call me a bum
all he wants.</b>

1161
01:15:10,402 --> 01:15:12,195
<b>Time to say good-bye.</b>

1162
01:15:14,407 --> 01:15:15,824
<b>Not coming up for your things?</b>

1163
01:15:16,074 --> 01:15:17,618
<b>I've got stuff at my place.
Tomorrow.</b>

1164
01:15:18,743 --> 01:15:20,829
<b>Well, good night, Elena.</b>

1165
01:15:21,080 --> 01:15:23,082
<b>I didn't think this 3 days ago.</b>

1166
01:15:23,749 --> 01:15:24,333
<b>What?</b>

1167
01:15:24,542 --> 01:15:26,502
<b>That I'd be sad to leave you.</b>

1168
01:15:27,753 --> 01:15:28,672
<b>Me neither.</b>

1169
01:15:33,218 --> 01:15:34,428
<b>Good night, Francois.</b>

1170
01:16:15,179 --> 01:16:16,472
<b>Am I bothering you?</b>

1171
01:16:16,722 --> 01:16:19,558
<b>No, I'm with my mom.
She quit drinking.</b>

1172
01:16:19,933 --> 01:16:20,517
<b>Yeah, when?</b>

1173
01:16:20,768 --> 01:16:22,686
<b>Today. Looks like it's working.</b>

1174
01:16:22,936 --> 01:16:24,605
<b>- You OK, Mom?
- I'm thirsty.</b>

1175
01:16:25,815 --> 01:16:29,693
<b>You can have this apartment:
I'm moving in with Emilie.</b>

1176
01:16:30,278 --> 01:16:31,779
<b>No way! That's so cool!</b>

1177
01:16:32,029 --> 01:16:34,865
<b>Elena there?
She can stay, wouldn't bother me.</b>

1178
01:16:35,115 --> 01:16:36,284
<b>No, she left.</b>

1179
01:16:36,534 --> 01:16:40,246
<b>To live with the man she loves,
and she's very happy.</b>

1180
01:16:40,622 --> 01:16:43,917
<b><i>Darling,
I never planned to divorce you.</b></i>

1181
01:16:44,918 --> 01:16:48,297
<b><i>You've been glum
since she lives with that guy.</b></i>

1182
01:16:48,506 --> 01:16:51,467
<b><i>She means nothing to me, it's over.</b></i>

1183
01:16:51,717 --> 01:16:53,343
<b><i>I'll go to Venice, but with you!</b></i>

1184
01:16:53,593 --> 01:16:55,304
<b><i>Once the Board meeting's over,</b></i>

1185
01:16:55,554 --> 01:16:58,474
<b><i>we'll leave on a second honeymoon.</b></i>

1186
01:17:14,198 --> 01:17:15,158
<b>Here she is.</b>

1187
01:17:45,648 --> 01:17:47,775
<b>- You?
- She's through with you.</b>

1188
01:17:48,359 --> 01:17:49,777
<b>Get out of this car!</b>

1189
01:17:49,986 --> 01:17:52,239
<b>- I have a message for you.
- Screw that!</b>

1190
01:17:52,655 --> 01:17:53,782
<b>Get him out!</b>

1191
01:17:54,033 --> 01:17:55,742
<b>- When do you go to Venice?
- What?</b>

1192
01:17:55,992 --> 01:17:58,454
<b>Hope you get the honeymoon suite.</b>

1193
01:17:58,829 --> 01:18:00,956
<b>No, wait! Take a walk.</b>

1194
01:18:03,292 --> 01:18:05,419
<b>I don't know what you're saying.</b>

1195
01:18:05,753 --> 01:18:07,755
<b>You will, in Venice with your wife.</b>

1196
01:18:09,214 --> 01:18:12,594
<b>I don't know how,
but you stole her, you creep!</b>

1197
01:18:13,094 --> 01:18:15,262
<b>I'm marrying
the girl I love in 3 weeks.</b>

1198
01:18:15,804 --> 01:18:17,807
<b>You can insult me all you want.</b>

1199
01:18:18,058 --> 01:18:20,017
<b>Elena says that, rich as you are,</b>

1200
01:18:20,226 --> 01:18:22,771
<b>you're a poor man!
She's sorry for you!</b>

1201
01:18:24,147 --> 01:18:26,775
<b>She won't get her 20 million,
I had it voided!</b>

1202
01:18:27,025 --> 01:18:29,487
<b>Not a penny, tell her!</b>

1203
01:18:29,903 --> 01:18:33,239
<b>She knew you'd cover yourself.
I'm sorry for you too!</b>

1204
01:18:47,505 --> 01:18:48,589
<b>Pignon!</b>

1205
01:19:01,186 --> 01:19:03,230
<b>Feeling blue? Want a little treat?</b>

1206
01:19:03,480 --> 01:19:04,940
<b>Leave me alone, dammit!</b>

